

'''= "SUPPORTING REGENERATIVE AGRICULTURE WITH OPEN SOURCE TOOLS".'''

URL = http://openagriculture.weebly.com/about.html

=Description=

"As agricultural producers and researchers attempt to shift agriculture towards more sustainable modes of production, there's an increasing need for research and monitoring tools that can provide them with real-time feedback. Current available options are often cost-prohibitive or designed specifically for researchers. We aim to develop, host, curate and promote open exchange of agricultural tools, software, and data to accelerate innovation and quantify environmental services from regenerative agriculture."
(http://openagriculture.weebly.com)


